title: William Howard Taft National Historic Site: Photo Gallery
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia     Photo Gallery              Photo Gallery       Official Photo Gallery of William Howard Taft National Historic Site                      Media Quality Centennial Photos   3 Photos  Hi-resolution photos relating to the park, for the public and the public media. All photos are in the public domain. Citations should be used if they are attached to the photos.          Great American Cleanup 2015   1 Photos  Various photos of park volunteers who spent the day cleaning up the grounds of the park during the 2015 Great American Cleanup.          100 years of Victorian Fashion   20 Photos  The impact of womens fashions and how they defined a woman. Fashion ashow and Wedding gown exhibit            Pictures for Research and Homework   8 Photos  Historical photos of the nation's 27th President and 10th Chief Justice of the Supreme Court.
